      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tlamantli huehueyac, pitzauctzin, mimiltic, tlacualtlalilli ica ichtli tlen quence pilmecatzitzin nochipa pilmecatzitzin momalintoc zancehco.</Note_Text>
